product.bullet_points:
• Premium Quality: The UPGRADE privacy screen for fences is made from 170 GSM non-recycled High-Density Polyethylene (HDPE). This ensures lasting durability, reliable privacy protection, and excellent weather resistance. A high-density composition makes it a dependable solution for outdoor privacy needs.
• Enhanced Privacy and Protection: UPGRADE Fence Privacy Screen offers up to 90% blackout, ensuring maximum privacy for your outdoor space. Shielded from harmful UV rays, enjoy complete seclusion while safeguarding your plants and flowers. Experience the perfect combination of privacy and protection with UPGRADE Fence Privacy Screen.
• Strong & Durable: The UPGRADE fence privacy screen boasts reinforced edges with double support on each side, complemented by anti-rust brass grommets. Count on long-lasting performance and tear resistance, ensuring your privacy solution stands the test of time. Enjoy peace of mind with the UPGRADE fence privacy screen's enhanced durability.
• Versatile Protection: The UPGRADE fence privacy screen excels in multiple applications. From safeguarding your yard and garden privacy to calming your pets and shielding plants from wind and animals, it's a perfect fit. It also serves construction sites, ensuring privacy and security throughout projects. Embrace the versatility of the UPGRADE fence privacy screen for various settings.
• Tailored to Your Needs: The UPGRADE fence privacy screen supports customization, allowing you to get the perfect fit for your unique requirements. Whether you need a specific size, color, or design, we've got you covered. Enjoy the freedom to personalize your privacy solution with UPGRADE fence privacy screen.
